What? That's disgusting.

189
00:27:41,263 --> 00:27:43,768
- She was his grandmother.
- Stepgrandmother...

190
00:27:43,936 --> 00:27:47,526
and still a young,
beautiful woman herself, don't forget.

191
00:27:47,691 --> 00:27:50,532
The prince, however, didn't like the idea.

192
00:27:55,541 --> 00:27:59,548
He took the famer's daughter,
and they rode away into the night.

193
00:28:02,470 --> 00:28:05,724
