227
00:30:21,209 --> 00:30:23,522
Farmers' daughters die for no reason.

228
00:30:23,764 --> 00:30:26,659
And sometimes witches merit saving.

229
00:30:27,444 --> 00:30:30,273
Quite often, actually. You'd be surprised.

230
00:30:32,661 --> 00:30:37,591
